{"tid":2208840,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★滙豐12月7日起　停滙豐控股及恒生兩股孖展借貸","createTime":"2020-09-19T08:21:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T05:24:21.000Z","uid":19454,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"a63035233bde5cc115a907b5e7435727c8acf24a","tid":2208840,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:21:27.000Z","msg":"滙豐銀行網站顯示，於12月7日起，將終止為滙豐控股(00005)及恒生(00011)兩隻股票提供孖展借貸。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐發言人表示，該行會不定期檢視股票孖展比率。滙豐控股和恒生銀行股票的孖展信貸將於12月7日起終止，建議客戶於3個月通知期內處理投資組合，該行職員將為客戶提供協助<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200918/bkn-20200918213217053-0918_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200918%2Fbkn-20200918213217053-0918_00842_001.html&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCvaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=2f37fbe2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200918/bkn-20200918213217053-0918_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"1141cd225075d8c649333a3ef0a54c83c555debb","tid":2208840,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:22:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4513169d0c972fd7ede5299adad102707cbfeef","tid":2208840,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:22:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rDra3dS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrDra3dS.png&h=5edf7b36&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"072cb56b45f9b38b14a8bcde40a08fbf0a6c6feb","tid":2208840,"uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:23:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj